            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Veneri <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>acrum</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>in <expan><abbr>memor</abbr><ex>iam</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Vib</abbr><ex>iae</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>Proculae ex tes<lb break="no" n="4"/>tamento <expan><abbr>Fl</abbr><ex>aviae</ex></expan> Tert<lb break="no" n="5"/>ullinae <expan><abbr>matr</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> de <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>lib</abbr><ex>ris</ex></expan> C <expan><abbr>Fl</abbr><ex>avii</ex></expan> Se<lb break="no" n="7"/>verus et Pud<lb break="no" n="8"/>entilla <expan><abbr>pos</abbr><ex>uerunt</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Consecratio in formam Veneris. Basis einer Bronzestatue. Hederae.</p>
            </div>
